	* unix/configure.in:	[Patch 2892871]: Remove unneeded
	* unix/tcl.m4:		AC_STRUCT_TIMEZONE and use
	* unix/tclConfig.h.in:	AC_CHECK_MEMBERS([struct stat.st_blksize])
