2009-08-25  Andreas Kupries  <andreask@activestate.com>

	* generic/tclBasic.c (Tcl_CreateInterp, Tcl_EvalTokensStandard)
	(Tcl_EvalEx, TclEvalEx, TclAdvanceContinuations, TclNREvalObjEx):
